reviewText: Very well put together and very Interesting
If you are interested in traveling and seeing some of the most beautiful places on earth, you will enjoy these beautifully photographed and fairly well narrated explorations of some of those places.
I love to walk and look at different scenes, and when I can't get out I love to watch  it on tv.
A wonderful overview and look at three different trails. As a hiker, I'm always interested in learning about new trails to hike.
I liked the scenic walks, but the video quality wasn't very good. Nice collection of scenic locations and views.
Another fine offering in this series... I greatly enjoyed the great photography and informative narrative
This was a nice, straight ahead review of scenic walks; no super-photogenic host, no jazzed up music, just a calm, thoughtful travelogue
